{
  "stem": "13833.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there is still a Swedish legation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You have to go there and speak to the ambassador.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And hopefully, they can bring them out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I told my parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "No, she can't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It's dangerous.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I looked at my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I said, I know it's dangerous, Mommy and Poppy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But they saved us all, 100,000 of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "How can I say no?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because what Raoul did at the last minute-- I forgot to tell you-- when he knew that the Russians are in there, one Hungarian who wanted him to help him came to him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he said, Raoul, I can just order to kill everybody in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We also had a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And there was 70,000 people in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on that day, it so happened two of  our Swedish Red Cross girls were in there delivering medication and letters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Raoul, without batting an eye, said go back to you headquarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tell them, the Germans, to called off the killing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the guns were standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Hungarian went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were in the office, and Raoul looks at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, now watch what I am going to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he picked up the phone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He spoke beautiful German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, this is Lieutenant Krausse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want to talk to General Schmidhuber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] When lieutenant want's to speak, they give it to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then he came to the phone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Raoul said, I am Raoul Wallenberg, and I am very, very disappointed in you, General.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I understand you are a highly decorated, First World War officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How can you take it on your heart to kill 70,000 innocent people plus my two Swedish Red Cross girls?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whereby the guy said, Eichmann ordered it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, Eichmann could have stood right with him, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
